exerciseStep: 1. Pull the bowls closer towards you with both of your hands.
2. With your right arm, pull the bowl on the right closer.
3. With your right arm, reach diagonally over to the last pole.
4. Use your left hand to grab the bowl on the side.
5. Use your right hand to grab the bowl on the side.
6. Stack the grabbed bowl on top of the one in the middle.
7. With your left hand, grab the bowl to the right.
8. With your right hand, grab the bowl to the right.
9. Place the bowl grabbed from the right to the middle.
10. Repeat the process of stacking bowls for two times in a row.
11. Place the stacked bowls anywhere on the table.
12. Repeat the entire process one more time.
